            <title><![CDATA[IPMC Hub 上线 —— 第一篇心得博客是这一篇]]></title>
            <link>https://ipmc-hub.org.cn/blog/welcome</link>
            <guid>https://ipmc-hub.org.cn/blog/welcome</guid>
            <pubDate>Sat, 30 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[欢迎来到 IPMC Hub 的心得博客区。]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>欢迎来到 IPMC Hub 的心得博客区。</p>
<p>这里是大家用<strong>个人视角</strong>记录学习生活的地方：阶段性复盘、比赛日记、面试回忆、获奖感言、日常感悟，都欢迎写在这里。</p>
<!-- -->
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="docs-vs-blog-怎么分">docs vs blog 怎么分<a href="https://ipmc-hub.org.cn/blog/welcome#docs-vs-blog-%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%88%86" class="hash-link" aria-label="docs vs blog 怎么分的直接链接" title="docs vs blog 怎么分的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>简单的判断方法：</p>
<ul>
<li class="">你想写**「这门课怎么学」**——属于 docs/courses，可以让下届直接照着学</li>
<li class="">你想写**「我学这门课的心路历程」**——属于 blog，是你的个人快照</li>
</ul>
<p>docs 是<strong>去人格化</strong>的教材；blog 是<strong>带温度</strong>的故事。两者都重要。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="怎么开始">怎么开始<a href="https://ipmc-hub.org.cn/blog/welcome#%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B" class="hash-link" aria-label="怎么开始的直接链接" title="怎么开始的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>参考 <a class="" href="https://ipmc-hub.org.cn/docs/contributing/quickstart">10 分钟提出第一个 PR</a>，把博客文件放在 <code>blog/&lt;YYYY-MM-DD&gt;-&lt;slug&gt;.md</code> 即可。</p>
<p>frontmatter 至少需要：</p>
<div class="language-yaml codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-yaml codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">---</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">slug</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> my</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain">first</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain">post</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">title</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> 我的第一篇博客</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">authors</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token plain">your</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token plain">id</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token key atrule" style="color:#00a4db">tags</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">[</span><span class="token plain">生活感悟</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">,</span><span class="token plain"> grade</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">-</span><span class="token number" style="color:#36acaa">2024</span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">]</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token punctuation" style="color:#393A34">---</span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="期待你的故事">期待你的故事<a href="https://ipmc-hub.org.cn/blog/welcome#%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%85%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B" class="hash-link" aria-label="期待你的故事的直接链接" title="期待你的故事的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>不必长篇大论，三百字也可以是一篇好文章。重要的是<strong>真实</strong>——告诉学弟学妹你真的踩过哪些坑、有过哪些转变。</p>
<hr>
<blockquote>
<p>这篇文章是项目占位说明，可以删除或替换。</p>
</blockquote>]]></content:encoded>
